# UI Rules

Follow [`DESIGN.md`](../../DESIGN.md) and [`docs/frontend.md`](../../docs/frontend.md).

- Anonymous UI: no avatars, usernames, or author identity on public content.
- Handle loading, empty, and error states on data-fetching views.
- Mobile-first responsive layouts; semantic color tokens for light/dark mode.
- Sanitize user-generated content before render.

